# Book Junk Away Meta Ad Studio — environment variables
#
# Copy to .env.local and fill in. None are required for the editor to run,
# but features degrade gracefully:
#   - Without GEMINI_API_KEY: Nano Banana image generation is disabled and
#     the natural-language Prompt Bar falls back to a heuristic builder.
#   - Without NEXT_PUBLIC_GIVEAWAY_WEBHOOK: share-to-win entries are saved
#     only to the recipient's local storage (you won't see them).

# Google Gemini API key (also accepts the GOOGLE_API_KEY alias)
# Get one at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional: POST every share-to-win entry to this URL as JSON.
# Use a Zapier/Make.com/n8n catch-hook to forward entries into your CRM,
# Google Sheet, or email.
NEXT_PUBLIC_GIVEAWAY_WEBHOOK=
